      <div class="meta">
        <h3><a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/hex-spell" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Theme Hive</a></h3>
        <p class="prompt">Hex-letter puzzle where valid words must match a daily theme (animals, foods, jobs). Theme banner up top. Found list grouped by length. Center letter mandatory.</p>
        <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/hex-spell" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Play live &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
  {{> newsletter}}
<footer>Built with vibes.diy. Each card is a one-prompt mini-app.</footer>
</div>
